org.activebpel.rt.bpel.config
Class AeDiffEngineConfiguration

java.lang.Object
  org.activebpel.rt.config.AeConfiguration
      org.activebpel.rt.bpel.config.AeDefaultEngineConfiguration
          org.activebpel.rt.bpel.config.AeDiffEngineConfiguration
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable, IAeEngineConfiguration, IAeUpdatableEngineConfig
public abstract class AeDiffEngineConfiguration
extends AeDefaultEngineConfiguration

This class implements an engine configuration that saves/loads a list of engine config differences rather than an entire engine config document. It is loaded first with a base config file, then a set of differences are applied to that base to get the final config. When saving the config, only those settings that are different from the base are saved.
